						 <p>The images that were used in this article are non-compliant with the SCP wiki's license (CC BY-SA 3.0) as the first was by artist Peter Gabriel (as indicated <a href="https://akrillics.tumblr.com/post/171239390976/redlipstickresurrected-peter-garfield-american">here</a>), with no indication it has been released under Creative Commons, and the second image comes from <a href="https://rosemaryfifieldblog.wordpress.com/">here</a> with no indication it has been released under Creative Commons. Thus, the images have been removed.</p> 
