				<pubDate>Thu, 03 Jan 2013 12:55:54 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Dr Lonewolf</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1300064</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Ok, so the flying houses gestate the egg, which then creates it's own mobile incubator. Have we left any -2 instances intact long enough to incubate?? I get that you have rotten/exploding eggs, good eggs and of course hostile/bad eggs. I wanna know what <em>kind</em> of eggs!!</p> <p>Also, what happens <em>inside</em> the houses during flight? Have we put cameras in the (supposedly unlocked) houses that have not gone -1? If so, why'd they fail? Always the questions&#8230;</p> <p>Awesomefantasticsuperb. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
