					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-517805#post-1503752</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-517805/scp-121#post-1503752</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 10 Jul 2012 05:35:01 +0000</pubDate>
								<wikidot:authorUserId>435193</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well, technically the -2s can get awfully dangerous, especially if they're aggressive and dangerous. Imagine a thirty-foot-tall junk monster with /guns/ built into it. And it has full control of those guns.</p> <p>But the idea was to make something that wasn't inherently aggressive, especially towards humans. While they can be, they don't become it &quot;just 'cause&quot;. But I'm glad you liked, and thanks!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
